ProtoDefines:
. "Let $\sigma$ be a permutation of the set $\{1, 2, \ldots, 
   n\}$. Then $i$ is a record of $\sigma$ if either $i = 1$ or 
   $\sigma(j) < \sigma(i)$ for every $j = 1,\ldots, i - 1$."
